The '''Aleen Classic''' was a [[Podracing/Legends|podracing]] event that took place annually on [[Aleen Minor/Legends|Aleen]], during the final years of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. One race was won by the [[Veknoid/Legends|Veknoid]] [[Podracer (profession)/Legends|podracer pilot]] [[Teemto Pagalies/Legends|Teemto Pagalies]], who used the prize money to free [[Trax Bonkik]] from [[Sebulba/Legends|Sebulba]].

